<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java" data-title="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">ArrayListDemo3</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
